            <h4>Education</h4>
<p>Fiskarfagskulen i Austevoll (Hordaland Upper Secondary School and Maritime Technical College) </p>
<h4>Job experience</h4>
<p>Worked as a fisherman for most of his working life. For three years he was a crane operator at a shipyard in Florø. </p>
<h4>Political experience</h4>
<p>Represented the Labour Party on the Flora Municipal Council for four terms and was a member of the Executive Committee of the Sogn og Fjordane Labour Party. </p>
<h4>Offices held</h4>
<p>Member of the National Executive Committee of the Norwegian Fishermen’s Association from 1986 to 1996, the last six years as vice president of the association. </p>
<p>President of the Sogn og Fjordane Fishermen’s Association from 1984 to 1994.</p>
<p>Member of the Board of the Norwegian Council for Fishery Research and on the Research Board for the Bioproduction and Processing Division of the Research Council of Norway.</p>
<p>For ten years was a member of the main board of the National Fishery Bank of Norway and chairman of the board for one year.</p>
